criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  1. ethnic Chinese;

          -  2. age, 18 to 65 years old;

          -  3. American Society of Anaesthesiologists (ASA) physical status I or II;

          -  4. Daytime patients scheduled for general anesthesia

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients unwilling to cooperate with the experiment

          -  Body mass index exceeding 30 kg/m2;

          -  Patients with a history of heart ,liver and Renal failure ,hypertension,diabetes
             mellitus or arteriosclerosis; and any allergy to drugs used in the study.

          -  Patients with the urinary diseases, such as kidney, ureteral calculi and tumors,
             prostatic hypertrophy.
